long_desc.thetext:
version 2.2 of Textile supports Textile comments / comment blocks.
The logic of these comments is explained here
http://textile.sitemonks.com/?eg=comments
After processing of the .textile files, the comments will simply be discarded.

Explanations on Textile comments from the 'original' PHP Textile developers:
http://txstyle.org/doc/40/textile-comments
Thansk for the bug. I've pushed an implementation https://git.eclipse.org/r/17784
